snippet.textDisplay: I'm just reading the responses to a lot of comments and it genuinely saddens me how mean and critical everyone is. Even if you want to call it clickbait, her not being completely honest about dying her hair isn't a big deal. You clearly watched the video because you enjoy her content, even if that means she just talks in front of the camera because that's what she does most of the time anyways. I don't understand the ability to sit here and make someone feel blatantly uncomfortable by expressing negative opinions, it's completely unnecessary. Regardless of her following, she is a human who has done absolutely nothing to you. She deserves to be treated like one. She didn't waste your time. Your time was already "wasted" by choosing to watch a video, regardless of the content it provided, rather than completing something that could be more productive.
